                        is_cover=False,
                        description="The ducks, injured in a car wreck in Southern California, are transported by means of a mysterious dream to the California of 1848. While there, they stay at the home of a wealthy Spanish rancher, take part in the gold rush, and help a young vaquero win the hand of a rancher’s daughter",
