                        is_cover=False,
                        description="A small planet is slipping closer and closer to earth, and the ducks are swept up in a storm caused by the planet’s approach. They land on a flying chariot and are taken to the planet, which is called Valhalla and is populated by Roman and Norse “gods.”",
